-- Wal-Mart recalls trail mix after reports of glass in product
-- 
-- Tue Jan 2, 2007 11:41am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/02/us-walmart-recall-idUSWNAS656120070102

 

 (Reuters) - Wal-Mart Stores Inc. ( WMT.N ) said it began a voluntary nationwide food product recall of certain lots of its store brand trail mix after reports of finding glass in the product. 

 Wal-Mart removed affected lots of Sam's Choice "Nature Trail" trail mix from sale. The product was supplied to Wal-Mart by Ann's House of Nuts, the world's biggest retailer said in a statement. (Reporting by Ankur Relia in Bangalore)